### QR Payment System - Analytics Testing
### VS Code REST Client File
### Extension: REST Client (by Huachao Mao)
### Run requests by clicking "Send Request" above each request

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@userEmail = john.kamau@email.com
@userPassword = password123
@vendorEmail = naivas.westlands@business.com
@vendorPassword = vendor123

###############################################
# 1. LOGIN AS USER
###############################################
# Click "Send Request" to login
# Copy the access_token from response
# Use it in the analytics requests below

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{userEmail}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}"
}

###############################################
# 2. GET USER ANALYTICS - FULL DASHBOARD
###############################################
# This shows EVERYTHING:
# - Overview (total spent, transaction count, average)
# - Top merchants (with business names and categories!)
# - Weekday patterns (which days you spend most)
# - Monthly trends (month by month breakdown)
# - Weekly breakdown (week by week)
# - Largest transactions (top 10 biggest payments)
# - Insights (personalized insights about spending)

GET {{baseUrl}}/user/analytics?days=30
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..r8y0aWzoI-i6vOeXLuLQ4MyvK3vyN-DyEZ7O2YdmD20
###############################################
# 3. GET USER ANALYTICS - CUSTOM TIME PERIODS
###############################################
# Test with different time ranges
# Try: ?days=60, ?days=90, ?months=6, ?weeks=8

GET {{baseUrl}}/user/analytics?days=60&months=6&weeks=8
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..gHN0Gh12q9JY1XgXuOJqzkOP8adVNxmSu-BL3aIPqaA
###############################################
# 4. LOGIN AS VENDOR
###############################################
# Click "Send Request" to login
# Copy the access_token from response
# Use it in the vendor analytics requests below

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{vendorEmail}}",
  "password": "{{vendorPassword}}"
}

###############################################
# 5. GET VENDOR ANALYTICS - FULL DASHBOARD
###############################################
# This shows EVERYTHING for vendor:
# - Cash flow (incoming vs outgoing money)
# - Net flow (profit/loss calculation with surplus/deficit)
# - Top customers (anonymized customer analytics)
# - Largest transactions (top 10 biggest payments received)
# - Outflow breakdown (where money goes: refunds, transfers, payouts, etc.)
# - Spending ratio (how much vendor retains vs spends)
# - Weekly performance (week-by-week comparison)

GET {{baseUrl}}/merchant/analytics?days=30
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..gHN0Gh12q9JY1XgXuOJqzkOP8adVNxmSu-BL3aIPqaA

###############################################
# 6. GET VENDOR ANALYTICS - CUSTOM TIME PERIODS
###############################################
# Test with different time ranges
# Try: ?days=60, ?days=90, ?weeks=8, ?weeks=12

GET {{baseUrl}}/merchant/analytics?days=90&weeks=12
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..gHN0Gh12q9JY1XgXuOJqzkOP8adVNxmSu-BL3aIPqaA

###############################################
# 7. GET USER PROFILE
###############################################
# Check user information

GET {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..gHN0Gh12q9JY1XgXuOJqzkOP8adVNxmSu-BL3aIPqaA

###############################################
# 8. GET USER TRANSACTIONS
###############################################
# See all transactions for the user with pagination

GET {{baseUrl}}/user/transactions?page=1&per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..gHN0Gh12q9JY1XgXuOJqzkOP8adVNxmSu-BL3aIPqaA
###############################################
# 9. GET VENDOR PROFILE
###############################################
# Check vendor information and business details

GET {{baseUrl}}/merchant/profile
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..gHN0Gh12q9JY1XgXuOJqzkOP8adVNxmSu-BL3aIPqaA
###############################################
# 10. GET VENDOR TRANSACTIONS
###############################################
# See all transactions for the vendor with pagination

GET {{baseUrl}}/merchant/transactions?page=1&per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..gHN0Gh12q9JY1XgXuOJqzkOP8adVNxmSu-BL3aIPqaA
###############################################
# NOTES FOR TESTING
###############################################
# 1. Run seed_data.py first to populate database
#    python seed_data.py
#
# 2. Start Flask app
#    python app.py
#
# 3. Step 1: Click "Send Request" on LOGIN AS USER (request #1)
#    This will return an access_token
#
# 4. Step 2: Copy the access_token value
#    It will be a long string in the response
#
# 5. Step 3: Replace the Authorization tokens in requests 2-3 with your token
#    Look for: Authorization: Bearer <paste_here>
#
# 6. Repeat for vendor login (request #4) for requests 5-6
#
# ALTERNATIVE: Use @token variable (easier)
# Uncomment the lines below after first login:
# @token = <paste_token_from_login_response>
# Then use: Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
#
# WHAT TO CHECK IN RESPONSES:
# ✅ User Analytics should show:
#    - top_merchants with business_name (e.g., "Naivas Supermarket")
#    - category from MCC (e.g., "Grocery Stores & Supermarkets")
#    - spending_summary with totals
#    - weekday_patterns (Sunday-Saturday)
#    - insights with personalized analysis
#
# ✅ Vendor Analytics should show:
#    - cash_flow (incoming vs outgoing)
#    - net_flow with status (surplus/deficit)
#    - top_customers (anonymized)
#    - outflow_breakdown by reason (refunds, transfers, etc.)
#    - spending_ratio showing retention percentage
#    - weekly_performance trends


###############################################
# 🔴 ADMIN ANALYTICS (NEW!)
###############################################

### ADMIN: Login (use user token for now, add admin later)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{userEmail}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}"
}

### ADMIN: Get Complete Dashboard Overview
# Shows: total vendors, total users, top vendors, top users, growth chart
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/metrics/overview?days=30
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE


### ADMIN: Get Merchant Insights
# Shows: top merchants by volume, top by success rate, total count
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/metrics/merchants?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE


### ADMIN: Get User Insights
# Shows: user growth over time, top active users, top spenders
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/metrics/users?days=30&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

